#    html/cmd_menu.media
#
# Purpose
#    Media fragment for cmd-menu
#
# Revision Dates
#    23-Nov-2011 (CT) Creation (factored from html/afs.jnj.media)
#     8-Apr-2013 (CT) Add `max_height` and `overflow_y` to `.cmd-menu`
